This person would have a good mind, and would be the perpetual student, always exploring and searching for hidden truths. Everything would be done on a “mental” plane, so little emotion would be displayed.  They would work best when left on their own, and the work would have to be of a specialised or analytical nature. They may give the impression of being somewhat aloof and unapproachable which could make it hard for others to get to know them.
